name: jupyter_console
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "5.0.0" %}

package:
  name: jupyter_console
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: jupyter_console-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://github.com/jupyter/jupyter_console/archive/{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: e966b2b5bf9a1e8c5bd11a6335bb11f68ec585ea39b801721b2ed9dd964468fa

build:
  number: 0
  script: python setup.py install
  entry_points:
    - jupyter-console = jupyter_console.app:main

requirements:
  build:
    - python
  run:
    - python
    - jupyter_client
    - ipython
    - ipykernel
    - prompt_toolkit
    - pygments
    - pexpect  # [not win]

test:
  commands:
    - jupyter-console -h
  imports:
    - jupyter_console

about:
  home: http://jupyter.org
  license: BSD 3-Clause
  summary: Jupyter terminal console

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - jakirkham
    - minrk
    - pelson
    - takluyver
    - ocefpaf
